跳<br />\n第二年再續牌，續牌費起跳同超速次數成 logarithmic 永久性遞增<br />\n如果果年再一次違規，下年 3600/yr<br />\n如果果年兩次違規，下年 5400/yr"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"除左以上懲罰性永久遞增人牌費，仲可以將汽車牌費按車齡比例性遞增，增加老爺車使用成本，少左老爺車又可以減番新車首次登記稅"},{"pid":"28681b861716b4ef1e0bd7e2f144db14c7491ff5","tid":981523,"uid":39551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"依家真係太多車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣出去又要排隊等車位<br />\n依家都係夜晩先會渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗等太耐"},{"pid":"a101b383b2fb722690e655221a9d1b812d17a3c8","tid":981523,"uid":173937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"其實最有效方法，真係設定某個入息以上先可以出車（跟報稅），變相會令政府稅收增加，因為好多人eg地盤或自僱，會報少入息，變相佢地想出車就要報返岩入息。另外住公屋個班，想出車亦只可報高入息，咁就可能有堆公屋會fee返出黎"},{"pid":"9da7aadbacb6870608985bf17360da19d3df3c8f","tid":981523,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28681b861716b4ef1e0bd7e2f144db14c7491ff5","tid":981523,"uid":39551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"依家真係太多車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣出去又要排隊等車位<br />\n依家都係夜晩先會渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗等太耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"邊樹要等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673846a38e20cb8ffc113698a6ca6d1249bb336f","tid":981523,"uid":39551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da7aadbacb6870608985bf17360da19d3df3c8f","tid":981523,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28681b861716b4ef1e0bd7e2f144db14c7491ff5","tid":981523,"uid":39551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"依家真係太多車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣出去又要排隊等車位<br />\n依家都係夜晩先會渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗等太耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201